data.title: Know Your State West Bengal
data.meta_description: Know Your State West Bengal - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a summary of the book "Know Your State West Bengal" which aims to provide comprehensive information about the Indian state of West Bengal. It includes chapters on the history, geography, climate, natural resources, industries, transportation, government and administration, districts, tourism, culture, and other topics relevant to the state. The summary is compiled by Goutam Chakraborty and Madhumita Pattrea to serve as a reference for students preparing for competitive exams in West Bengal.
